这时 $a_{i-2}$ 只能为 $1$  
$f_{i,0,0} = f_{i-1,0,1}$ 

② $a_i = 0,a_{i-1} = 1$   
这时 $a_{i-2} = 0/1$  
$f_{i,0,1} = f_{i-1,1,0} + f_{i-1,1,1}$  

③ $a_i = 1,a_{i-1} = 0$  
这时 $a_{i-2} = 0/1$  
$f_{i,1,0} = f_{i-1,0,0} + f_{i-1,0,1}$  

④ $a_i = 1,a_{i-1} = 1$  
这时 $a_{i-2} = 0/1$  
$f_{i,1,1} = f_{i-1,1,0} + f_{i-1,1,1}$
